Cyrillic (windows-1251) fonts for MPlayer
=========================================

These font sets were generated using TOOLS/subfont-c from MPlayer package.
Parameter scripts (gen/gen_fonts.sh) is included.


How to install the install
--------------------------

To install the fonts select font size and copy the content of the directory
to ~/.mplayer/font/ (for single user installation) or in /usr/local/share/mplayer/font


Example installation
--------------------

   cp arial-18/* ~/.mplayer/font/
   su -c "cp arial-18/* /usr/local/share/mplayer/font/"


Font are generated by Georgi Chorbadzhiyski <georgi@unixsol.org>
Web page: http://georgi.unixsol.org/
